title: Flash Games - Zombie Pack
description:
This is a collection of flash zombie games.  Open with internet explorer, firefox, or chrome.  Must have Flash installed.  To install flash go to http://get.adobe.com/flashplayer/ .  I know you can just go to a website and play these but you never know when you might want to play a quick game on your laptop when your not around internet.  These are quick and take up no space at all.
